 20.11 \u201CProfessional Services\u201D means consulting services provided by Fathym, whether standard or customized.  

 20.12 \u201CRecipient\u201D means the party receiving Confidential Information under this Agreement.  

 20.13 \u201CServices\u201D means Subscriptions, Professional Services, Training Services, access to Fathym Online Properties or other services offered or made available by Fathym.  

 20.14 \u201CSoftware\u201D means Fathym branded software.
